         <div id="tab4"> 
          <h3>Contact</h3> 
          <p>     </p>
          <p><strong>Environmental, Health and Safety Committee</strong><br><br><strong>Contact EHS</strong>&nbsp;<br>Email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:ehs@greenriver.edu">ehs@greenriver.edu</a><br><br><strong>Campus Safety</strong><br>In person: Administration Building&nbsp;<br>Phone: 253-288-3350 or extension 3350 or 2250&nbsp;<br>Email:&nbsp;<a href="Mailto:safety@greenriver.edu">safetydispatch@greenriver.edu</a><br><br><strong>To report an accident or near-miss, contact Human Resources</strong><br>In person: Human Resources Building&nbsp;<br>Phone: 253-833-9111, ext. 2599<br>Email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:tturner@greenriver.edu">tturner@greenriver.edu</a> <br><a href="mailto:hr@greenriver.edu" title="HR email"></a></p>  
